<style>
    body {
       font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
       background-color: #f5f5f5;
       margin: 0;
       padding: 0;
    }
    .header {
       background-color: #24292e;
       color: white;
       padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
       margin: 0;
       font-size: 2.5em;
       text-align: center;
       color: rgb(22, 188, 230);
    }
    .task {
       border: 2px solid #616364;
       border-radius: 10px;
       margin: 20px;
       padding: 20px;
       background-color: #fff;
    }
    .task h2 {
       font-size: 1.5em;
       margin-top: 0;
       margin-bottom: 10px;
       color: #24292e;
    }
    .task p {
       font-size: 1.2em;
       margin-top: 0;
       margin-bottom: 20px;
       color: #616364;
    }
    .task ul {
       list-style-type: none;
       padding: 0;
       margin: 0;
    }
    .task li {
       font-size: 1.2em;
       margin-bottom: 10px;
       color: #616364;
    }
    .task a {
       color: #4992db;
       font-weight: bold;
       text-decoration: none;
    }
    .task a:hover {
       color: #003366;
    }
    .task-submission {
       margin: 20px;
       padding: 20px;
       background-color: #fff;
    }
    .task-submission h2 {
       font-size: 1.5em;
       margin-top: 0;
       margin-bottom: 20px;
       color: #24292e;
    }
    .task-submission form {
       margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .task-submission label {
       font-size: 1.2em;
       color: #616364;
    }
    .task-submission input[type="text"],
    .task-submission input[type="email"],
    .task-submission input[type="url"],
    .task-submission select {
       width: 100%;
       padding: 10px;
       font-size: 1em;
       border: 1px solid #ccc;
       border-radius: 4px;
       margin-top: 5px;
       margin-bottom: 15px;
       box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .task-submission button {
       padding: 10px 20px;
       font-size: 1em;
       border: none;
       border-radius: 4px;
       background-color: #4992db;
       color: white;
       cursor: pointer;
    }
    .task-submission button:hover {
       background-color: #003366;
    }
    .footer {
       background-color: #24292e;
       color: white;
       padding: 10px;
       text-align: center;
    }
 </style>
 <div class="header">
    <h1>DSA Tasks</h1>
 </div>
 <div class="task">
    <h2>Task 1</h2>
    <p>Create your account on <a href="https://www.hackerrank.com/" target="_blank">HackerRank</a> and start solving questions on your language choice.</p>
    <ul>
       <li>Language choice: C++/Java/Python.</li>
       <li>Minimum criteria to get marks: 4-star rating on HackerRank for any language.</li>
       <li>After completing the minimum criteria, submit your user profile link on the task submission form below.</li>
       <li>Max Marks: 15/100.</li>
       <li>Ideal Time Required: 1 week</li>
    </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="task">
    <h2>Task 2</h2>
    <p>Solve DSA Topic On HackerRank.</p>
    <ul>
       <li>Minimum criteria to get marks: solve DSA questions daily and score up to 3 stars.</li>
       <li>After completing the minimum criteria, submit your user profile link on the task submission form below.</li>
       <li>Max Marks: 25/100.</li>
       <li>Ideal Time Required: 2 weeks</li>
    </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="task">
    <h2>Task 3</h2>
    <p>Solve Problem Solving Topic on HackerRank.</p>
    <ul>
       <li>Minimum criteria to get marks: Solve problem-solving questions and score up to 3 stars.</li>
       <li>After completing the minimum criteria, submit your user profile link on the task submission form below.</li>
       <li>Max Marks: 25/100.</li>
       <li>Ideal Time Required: 2 weeks</li>
    </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="task">
    <h2>Task 4</h2>
    <p>Solve DSA problems and participate in contests on Leetcode</p>
    <ul>
       <li>Minimum criteria to get marks: Solve daily DSA problems, maintain your streak, participate in contests, and upgrade your profile ranking.</li>
       <li>Your profile ranking should be under 1.5 lakh to be eligible for marks.</li>
       <li>After completing the minimum criteria, submit your user profile link on the task submission form below.</li>
       <li>Max Marks: 35/100.</li>
       <li>Ideal Time Required: 3 to 4 weeks</li>
    </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="task-submission">
    <h2>Task Submission</h2>
    <form id="taskSubmissionForm" action="/submit-dsatask" method="POST">
       <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="task">Task</label>
          <select id="task" name="task" required>
             <option value="">Select a task</option>
             <option value="Task 1">Task 1 - Language practice</option>
             <option value="Task 2">Task 2 - DSA</option>
             <option value="Task 3">Task 3 - Problem Solving</option>
             <option value="Task 4">Task 4 - Leetcode contests</option>
          </select>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="hackerrankLink">HackerRank Profile Link</label>
          <input type="url" id="hackerrankLink" name="hackerrankLink" placeholder="Enter the HackerRank profile link" required>
       </div>
       <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="leetcodeLink">Leetcode Profile Link</label>
          <input type="url" id="leetcodeLink" name="leetcodeLink" placeholder="Enter the Leetcode profile link" required>
       </div>
       <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
 </div>
